&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join Our Team as an Emergency Veterinarian at Coral Springs Animal Hospital!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
