&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quo

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Join Our Team as an Emergency Veterinarian at &lt;strong&gt;Quartet Veterinary Specialty Hospital!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quartet Veterinary Specialty Hospital (Cary, NC)&lt;/strong&gt; is seeking an &lt;strong&gt;Emergency Veterinarian&lt;/strong&gt; to help grow and expand our newly established urgent care service into a full service ER. This marks the next phase of our planned expansion into a full 24/7 Emergency Service, further elevating the continuity and accessibility of advanced veterinary care in the area. This is a unique opportunity to join a respected specialty hospital at a pivotal moment of expansion and to play a key role in shaping the future of emergency medicine at Quartet.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Us?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;State-of-the-Art Facilities&lt;/strong&gt;: Our hospital is equipped with modern amenities, providing a comfortable and efficient workspace for our team. Our facility is part of our ongoing commitment to investing in the best tools for our staff and patients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Established Excellence&lt;/strong&gt;: With over 25 years of serving the Research Triangle region, our hospital has cultivated strong, loyal relationships with referring veterinarians and clients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative Expertise&lt;/strong&gt;: Join a team featuring the region&#39;s most experienced surgeons, supported by a residency-trained anesthesia doctor and skilled RVT staff. Our environment thrives on mentorship, teamwork, and collaboration.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Supportive Environment&lt;/strong&gt;: Enjoy a Fear-Free certified approach to patient care and a close-knit team that prioritizes professional growth, wellness, and mutual support.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Freedom to Grow:&lt;/strong&gt; Unique opportunity to be part of shaping and building the emergency medicine department. &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Living in Cary, NC&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Cary is centrally located in the heart of the Triangle Region, known for its thriving economy, excellent public schools, and vibrant community. Whether you&#39;re a foodie, sports fan, outdoor enthusiast, or cultural connoisseur, Cary offers something for everyone. With its family-friendly atmosphere and proximity to Raleigh, Durham, and Chapel Hill, it&#39;s the perfect place to live and work.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
