&lt;li&gt;Practice safe handling techniques of animal patients during exams and procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collect diagnostic samples for in-house testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a clean and organized hospital environment including cleaning kennels and treatment areas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restock supplies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow proper sanitation and sterilization protocols. Compassion and professionalism are essential as you interact with clients, comfort patients, and collaborate with your team. Additional duties may be assigned to support the overall care and efficiency of the hospital.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
