&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 1 year veterinary hospital experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An ability to manage time and priorities with minimal direct supervision&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Punctuality and exceptional attendance&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A willingness to work non-traditional hours such as weekends, evenings, and a share of holidays&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
