&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A place to grow: &lt;/strong&gt;Our commitment to training and Medical Advancement means you’ll have the opportunity to grow your skills and knowledge as well as providing a path for advancing your career. &lt;strong&gt;Continuing education allowance&lt;/strong&gt; for assistants&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;and&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;credentialed technicians.&lt;/li&gt;
