&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Friendship Hospital for Animals, &lt;/strong&gt;a leading AAHA- accredited hospital located in &lt;strong&gt;Washington D.C.&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;nbsp;is seeking friendly and enthusiastic Veterinary Customer Service Representatives to support our thriving primary care, emergency, and specialty teams. If you have strong communication skills and want to work as a part of a collaborative and diverse team – we’d love to meet you!&lt;/p&gt;
