&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet Our Surgical Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll be joining one of the most experienced surgical teams in the Research Triangle area, with decades of combined experience and a stellar reputation for exceptional patient care. Our anesthesia service is led by an anesthesia residency-trained doctor, supported by a highly skilled and dedicated RVT team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our caseload includes a balanced mix of orthopedic, soft tissue, and neurosurgical cases, supported by advanced technology and diagnostics, including:&lt;/p&gt;
