&lt;li&gt;Arthroscopy and laparoscopy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;C-arm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ethicon Enseal and Ligasure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ultrasonography available in-house&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MRI capability available through a contracted partner&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our long-standing referral relationships provide a robust, steady surgical caseload, allowing you to focus on practicing excellent medicine without the pressure of building volume.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Culture&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Quartet, collaboration and respect define how we work together. Our team is close-knit, supportive, and genuinely enjoys what we do. We value mentorship, open communication, and strong relationships—with each other, with our referring veterinarians, and with our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Team culture extends beyond the clinic, with regular opportunities to connect through potlucks, celebrations, lunches, and shared enthusiasm for college and professional sports. We believe great medicine happens when people feel supported and balanced.&lt;/p&gt;
