&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join Our Team at Coral Springs Animal Hospital!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you a dedicated and compassionate professional who thrives in a surgical environment and takes pride in precision and organization? We are seeking a dedicated &lt;strong&gt;Veterinary Surgical Pack &amp;amp; Prep Assistant&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing specialty surgery team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coral Springs Animal Hospital is a state‑of‑the‑art, AAHA‑certified facility in South Florida offering primary care, specialty services, and 24/7 emergency care. &lt;/strong&gt;Our compassionate team collaborates across multiple disciplines—from oncology and surgery to radiology, ultrasound, and rehabilitation—delivering advanced diagnostics and treatments using cutting‑edge equipment. We’re dedicated to fostering a supportive environment where veterinary professionals can grow, feel empowered, and make a meaningful difference in pet lives daily.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Can Expect to Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our ideal candidate takes pride in maintaining sterility, organization, and efficiency in the surgical suite. Our team members understand that behind every successful surgery is meticulous preparation and attention to detail. They are motivated, reliable, and proactive individuals who work well in a fast-paced, team-oriented environment and are eager to learn specialty surgical procedures and protocols.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Surgery Pack &amp;amp; Prep Assistant, &lt;/strong&gt;responsibilities include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;cleaning, assembling, labeling, and sterilizing surgical instrument packs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;maintaining surgical suite cleanliness, organization, and readiness for procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;assisting with pre-operative patient preparation as directed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;operating and maintaining sterilization equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;restocking and tracking surgical supplies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;accurately documenting sterilization and inventory logs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience in a veterinary, medical, or surgical setting is preferred, though we are willing to train the right candidate with strong attention to detail and a willingness to learn.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable around animals, with a passion for their health and well being&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Us?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remarkable Culture&lt;/strong&gt; – We value teamwork, mutual respect, and professional growth. Our hospital fosters a learning-focused environment where team members are supported, encouraged, and given opportunities to expand their skills within specialty medicine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work-life Rewards&lt;/strong&gt; – We offer competitive compensation based on experience, paid time off, medical, dental, and vision benefits, employee pet care discounts, continuing education opportunities, and more.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work-Life Balance&lt;/strong&gt; – We are committed to supporting the well-being of our team members with structured schedules and a positive work environment that values balance and sustainability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Career Advancement Opportunities&lt;/strong&gt; – We believe in growing from within and supporting long-term career development in specialty veterinary medicine.&lt;/p&gt;
